# 🚀 CareerOS

> Personal Career Management Dashboard for IT Professionals

CareerOS is a personal web application that helps manage the entire IT career journey in one place.

It combines job applications, learning progress, daily tasks, portfolio tracking, interview preparation, and career planning into a single dashboard.

