## ✨ Features

### Dashboard

- Career statistics
- Active job application
- Learning progress
- Daily tasks
- Quick navigation

### Jobs Manager

- Create jobs
- Edit jobs
- Delete jobs
- Search
- Filter
- LocalStorage persistence

### Tasks Manager

- Create tasks
- Edit tasks
- Delete tasks
- Mark completed
- Search
- Filter
- LocalStorage persistence

### Learning Center *(planned)*

- Track learning progress
- Study resources
- Notes
- Progress statistics

